courses.subject: GE
courses.customDesc: One course from each of the following GE areas must be completed: A1, A2, A3, Upper-Division B, C1, Upper-Division C, F, and GE Elective. Upper-Division B, Upper-Division C, and Upper-Division D (GEOG308) should be taken only after Junior standing is reached (90 units). NOTE: Some GE may be fulfilled in concentration courses or minors. Refer to online catalog for GE course selection and Graduation Writing Requirement (GWR).
